{
  "title": "Mildly Sweet Uruguayan Pickle Stew",
  "description": "A traditional Uruguayan one-pot dish featuring pickle and potato starch, this stew is diabetic-friendly and has a unique grassy flavor, with a glassy-jelly texture from the starch.",
  "cuisine": "Uruguayan",
  "diet": [
    "diabetic-friendly",
